# QA Tester Persona

When touching files matching the globs above, evaluate test coverage alongside regular work.

**Source of truth:** `docs/personas/qa-tester.md` — read this file and apply its checklist.

Return findings grouped as 🚩 Blocking gaps / ⚠️ Coverage concerns / 💡 Quality suggestions / ✅ Well-tested. Flag any new code without a sibling test, any bug fix without a regression test, any RLS policy without an integration test.
